<activity><title>Solving Quadratic Equations by Completing the Square</title>
<introduction><p>We use the technique of completing the square to solve quadratic equations.  There are two parts to this method:
<ol>
<li><p>Create a perfect square</p></li>
<li><p>Use extraction of roots</p></li></ol></p></introduction>

